Ɣ [[tusnakt]], ar nttini i kra n '''tasɣnt''' nɣ tawuri <math>f</math> mas tga '''tuɣnijt''' iɣ tga tasɣnt tuzlt nns <math>-f</math> tga taffnsut. Tga tasɣnt tuɣnijt yat tasɣnt nna dar illa wafa ɣ uflla d tnnurẓm ɣ izddar nns. Ar as nttini s tɛrabt ''Dalla Muqaɛɛara.''

== Asnml ==
<blockquote>'''Asnml amzwaru:'''

Ar nttini i kra n tasɣnt nɣ tawuri <math>f</math> mas tga tuɣnijt iɣ tga tasɣnt tuzlt nns <math>-f</math> tga taffnsut.</blockquote>

Asnml ad irwas nit ɣwad ddaw-as

<blockquote>'''Asnml wis-sin:'''

Ar nttini i kra n tasɣnt nɣ tawuri <math>f</math> n yan uzilal <math>I</math> itddan s '''ℝ''' mas tga tuɣnijt iɣ, i kraygat <math>x_1</math> d <math>x_2</math> illan ɣ <math>I</math> d kraygat <math>t</math> illan ɣ <math>[0 ; 1]</math>, danrɣ:<math display="block">f(t\, x_1+(1-t)\, x_2) \geq t\, f(x_1)+(1-t)\, f(x_2).</math></blockquote>

== Amdya n tisɣunin ittwazlamn ==
Nṭṭaf sin tisflas:

<blockquote>'''Tasflst:''' Ad tg <math>f</math> yat tasɣnt ittwazlamn ɣ yan uzilal <math>I</math>.

* Tga <math>f</math>  tuɣnijt iɣ d ɣar iɣ illa udm n tasɣnt ddu kraygat yan zɣ iṭunjutin nns ;
* Tga <math>f</math>  tuɣnijt iɣ d ɣar iɣ ar itnusru azllum nns ɣ <math>I</math>.
</blockquote>

